I absolutely love Timbuk 3 and consider them to be a heinously underrated band. A torrent of their discography has been available here on TPB for some time now, but not all of the albums in that upload are high quality mp3 files. So I took it upon myself to scour the internet for better quality material.
Three of their albums (‘Greetings From Timbuk 3,’ ‘Eden Alley,’ and ‘Edge of Allegiance’) I found on(many thanks to users marksman and Hudok for uploading those albums). The ‘Live From Austin City Limits’ album I found on newalbumreleases.net, and ‘Some of the Best of Timbuk 3: Field Guide’ I took from the above-mentioned discography torrent. The rest of the albums were ripped by me personally.
It didn’t require hours and hours of exertion, but I did put some effort into compiling this torrent, so I hope the people that download it really enjoy it. And I know this will mostly fall on deaf ears since the majority of people are selfish and greedy, but please seed. You would never complete a download if no one seeded, so be considerate and return the favor
